'''70亿人口日'''，即2011年10月31日，这一天[[世界人口|世界人口]]近似达到70亿人，这是由[[联合国人口基金会|联合国人口基金会]]（United Nations Population Fund，UNFPA）正式指定的日子<ref name=un>[http://esa.un.org/unpd/wpp/Other-Information/faq.htm World Population Prospects, the 2008 Revision Frequently Asked Questions] {{Wayback|url=http://esa.un.org/unpd/wpp/Other-Information/faq.htm |date=20150224215308 }} Population Division of the Department of Economic and Social Affairs of the United Nations Secretariat updated 10 November 2010. Retrieved 26 January 2011</ref>。[[联合国秘书长|联合国秘书长]][[潘基文|潘基文]]在位于[[纽约|纽约]]的[[联合国总部大楼|联合国总部大楼]]宣布这个-{}-里程碑日子的到来，并发起“70亿人行动倡议”<ref name="unfpa">{{cite web|url=https://www.unfpa.org/public/home/news/events/pid/8533|title=Day of 7 Billion|publisher=UNFPA|accessdate=16 October 2011|archive-date=2011-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111107210531/http://www.unfpa.org/public/home/news/events/pid/8533|dead-url=no}}</ref>，让人们了解70亿人口带来的机会与挑战，并激励各国政府、非政府组织以及个人等采取行动<ref name="actions">{{cite web |url=http://www.7billionactions.org/about |title=About 7 Billion Actions |publisher=7 Billion Actions |accessdate=16 October 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111024144450/http://www.7billionactions.org/about |archivedate=2011-10-24 }}</ref>。

